<p rend="centre"> Namo tassa bhagavato arahato sammāsambuddhassa</p>

<p rend="book">Paramatthadīpanī</p>

<p rend="title">Saṅgaha mahāṭīkā pāṭha</p>

<p rend="subsubhead">Ganthārabbhakathā</p>

<p rend="bodytext">[Ka]</p>

<p rend="gatha1">Udayā <pb ed="M" n="0.0001" /> yassa ekassa, saddhammaraṃsi jālino;</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Pabujjhiṃsu janambujā, jātikkhette mahāsare.</p>

<p rend="bodytext">[Kha]</p>

<p rend="gatha1">Vandāmi taṃ mahāsūraṃ, mahāmoha tamonudaṃ;</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Sañjātaṃ so hadaye mayhaṃ, tamokhandhaṃ panūdataṃ.</p>

<p rend="bodytext">[Ga]</p>

<p rend="gatha1">Porāṇakehi viññūhi, vaṇṇitā vaṇṇanā bahū;</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Dissanti idha lokamhi, abhidhammatthasaṅgahe.</p>

<p rend="bodytext">[Gha]</p>

<p rend="gatha1">Na tāhi tuṭṭhiṃ vindanti, ye sāratthā bhimānino;</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Te maṃ saṅgamma yācanti, paramatthassa dīpanaṃ.</p>

<p rend="bodytext">[Ṅa]</p>

<p rend="gatha1">Mahaṇṇave ratanāni, uddharitvā dipavāsinaṃ;</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Yathicchakaṃpi dajjeyyuṃ, na vattabbāva ūnatā.</p>

<p rend="bodytext">[Ca]</p>

<p rend="gatha1">Tathevettha <pb ed="M" n="0.0002" /> vipulatthā, aṇṇave ratanūpamā;</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Satakkhattuṃpi vaṇṇeyyuṃ, pariyādinnā na hessare.</p>

<p rend="bodytext">[Cha]</p>

<p rend="gatha1">Tasmā tāsu vaṇṇanāsu, sāramādāya vaṇṇanaṃ;</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Nānāsārattha sampuṇṇaṃ, uttāna padabyañjanaṃ.</p>

<p rend="bodytext">[Ja]</p>

<p rend="gatha1">Nātisaṅkhepa vitthāraṃ, mandabuddhippabodhanaṃ;</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Karissaṃ taṃ paramatthesu, suṇantu pāṭavatthinoti.</p>
